      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it is pristine inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love the moment you see it!",
