    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for showroom condition. This car has been meticulously garaged since day one, preserved in a climate-controlled environment to maintain its flawless, deep-gloss finish. The exterior is free of even the slightest stone chips or swirl marks, reflecting a mirror-like shine that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has never seen a drop of rain or winter salt, ensuring the undercarriage is as pristine as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
